{"tid":2253924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"其實有幾多人知匯豐隻銅獅，一早比支共偷左上博物館","createTime":"2020-10-22T13:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T21:13:41.000Z","uid":134093,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb84cf015bae3d7875680fbfab31d6d71cbd8de0","tid":2253924,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"置放在總行門前的這兩頭雄獅，張嘴吼叫的是「史提芬」（Stephen），此名得自1920年－1924年的香港總行總司理史提芬（Alexander G. Stephen），而鑄造銅獅也來自他的倡議。另一頭銅獅稱為「施迪」（Stitt），是當時以1921年上海司理施迪（Gordon H. Stitt）的名字命名。<br />\n<br />\n原件「史提芬」在上海外灘的東方明珠廣播電視塔內的<span class=\"red\">上海城市歷史發展陳列館中展覽</span>。另外一隻「施迪」則存放在<span class=\"red\">上海市銀行博物館</span>。在2007年11月28日至2008年3月24日期間，上海把「施迪」借予香港歷史博物館來舉行專題展覽「從錢莊到現代銀行：滬港銀行業發展」。<br />\n<br />\n仲借返比你香港展覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedbe21f060a946e239cb1ed763311649f5687f7","tid":2253924,"uid":134093,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"香港嗰兩隻翻版<br />\n點樣開光都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b793ee425da281c9c95b5c3feeb495748db1709","tid":2253924,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9569dc529d52c395e806f03a717148069d67c1","tid":2253924,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80329c6f6ff0a0484a31c2ecc95467d9a0c8b4ff","tid":2253924,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"即係香港嗰隻燒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28afc74e1bd14bb111bc70267f293e5352b0f58f","tid":2253924,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09375160d425f86c9e84e9ecfca6234c0fb74fb9","tid":2253924,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"反正都共過一次產，共多次有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a6262ccd169a4fdf856488f417bab45e84245d","tid":2253924,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"做場戲自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25a152d1a30dc87657bd234bdf99ed8b8e9d4b6","tid":2253924,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"老點下啲遊客<br />\n賺錢又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e033d988e73794237925e96be4e38ecde701b77e","tid":2253924,"uid":4811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"原來真獅王一早被人擄走咗，困係上海，怪之得未好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe9b1a3b227258738a002c71ba011d1803a848a","tid":2253924,"uid":47462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"得支那先咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15900c924a8e5c95b19023eaaddb6014fa19329d","tid":2253924,"uid":181557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T21:08:28.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n第二代（1935年）：仿照於第一代原品仿製，每隻重2250磅；置放在香港滙豐總行大廈門前<br />\n第五代（2015年）：為慶祝滙豐成立150周年，滙豐仿照香港總行的一對複製，並安放在位於西九龍大角咀的後勤總部滙豐中心地下大堂。<br />\n英國<br />\n第三代（2001年）：仿照於第二代香港銅獅製作，在英國倫敦金絲雀碼頭（Canary Wharf, London）的滙豐集團新總部大廈門前。<br />\n第六代（2018年）：滙豐再仿照香港滙豐總行的一對複製，並安放在位於伯明罕的英國滙豐銀行總部大樓外。<br />\n中國<br />\n第一代（1923年）：現存放在上海市銀行博物館。<br />\n仿製品（1997年）：在上海浦東發展銀行於1997年獲得前上海滙豐銀行大樓的使用權後，照第一代原樣鑄造了兩尊新銅獅置放在原位。上海浦東發展銀行曾希望將原品從上海博物館移回銀行大門前，後經協商，由銀行方面出資重新鑄造，在仿鑄造過程中，出於對歷史的尊敬，原日軍破壞的鋸痕也一併保留呈現。<br />\n第四代（2009年）：選用香港滙豐總行大廈外的一對作藍本，這對銅獅現在按照傳統安放在滙豐中國總部、上海國際金融中心的滙豐銀行大樓外。"},{"pid":"dce861c4d875d8933a6d0e10675e6064353a83aa","tid":2253924,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T21:13:41.000Z","msg":"共產黨不滅，必禍害全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}